of an insignificant man like me.

579
00:33:01,239 --> 00:33:02,000
What are you planning to do?

580
00:33:02,959 --> 00:33:03,599
I'm entering the imperial palace

581
00:33:04,359 --> 00:33:05,239
to ask for a position.

582
