Are you planning to
threaten His Majesty?

583
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:09,599
Are you serious?

584
00:33:39,439 --> 00:33:40,000
Xiaoman.

585
00:33:46,760 --> 00:33:47,439
Congwen.

586
00:33:49,560 --> 00:33:50,319
Are you all right?

587
00:33:51,479 --> 00:33:52,040
I'm fine.

588
